{"tid":2248205,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普聽鷹派建議加碼抗中","createTime":"2020-10-18T12:09:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T12:24:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2254a0a007b400c8eb26588cbbbb821de31dae1c","tid":2248205,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T12:09:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201018/RKIHS47JCJALZFSX3ZIMUGJS4U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201018%2FRKIHS47JCJALZFSX3ZIMUGJS4U%2F&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1axVTfDkzAunSCULMKrq9Td0%3D&h=c46fd0d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201018%2FRKIHS47JCJALZFSX3ZIMUGJS4U%2F&h=b197d63e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201018/RKIHS47JCJALZFSX3ZIMUGJS4U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n特朗普聽鷹派建議加碼抗中<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ZHpmXNGg1OaOr4hZVP8hEXWM_QY=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TVNHEHVZT5HLXHVXXJGJI5C5SI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZHpmXNGg1OaOr4hZVP8hEXWM_QY%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTVNHEHVZT5HLXHVXXJGJI5C5SI.jpg&h=0b9f8027&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中美關係近月迅速惡化，特朗普跟習近平沒有再接觸。<br />\n<br />\n【美總統大選】《華爾街日報》前日報道，美國總統特朗普在大選年猛打抗中牌，鷹派幕僚在武漢肺炎疫情爆發後成功游說是關鍵；美方考慮使出更多手段，包括監視在美國支援間諜工作的中國國營航空公司員工。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：吸1,410萬觀眾 拜登收視小勝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n監視涉諜中國國航員工<br />\n<br />\n報道引述美國多名現任與前任官員報道，特朗普2017年上任後，國家安全團隊中許多人欲對抗中國；但三年過去，特朗普未將中國視為最大威脅，且將美中貿易談判視為優先，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n多名官員指，華府考慮使出更多手段，包括監視疑似在美國支援諜報工作的中國國營航空公司員工、。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。；武肺從中國向外蔓延後，特朗普身邊的對華鷹派幕僚佔上風；北京當局在香港等地的強勢作為激怒美方官員和國會。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，無論特朗普或前副總統拜登贏得今屆總統選舉，美中對抗局勢都不大可能降溫。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美國《華爾街日報》"},{"pid":"00b14a07d49e41e5f16d13b7bb30f375a61192c3","tid":2248205,"uid":360777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T12:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}